amount field has been removed as part of US 625960 since the logic was updating all Optum Reversal Claims historically taking ~15 minutes for each run. \n\nThe logic is now handled in IdsEdwDrugClmPriceFExtr xfm_BusinessLogic\n\nUPDATE #$EDWOwner#.DRUG_CLM_PRICE_F DFUP\nSET DFUP.CALC_SELL_INGR_CST_AMT = DF.CALC_SELL_INGR_CST_AMT * -1,\nDFUP.CALC_BUY_INGR_CST_AMT = DF.CALC_BUY_INGR_CST_AMT * -1,\nDFUP.CALC_GUAR_RBT_AMT = DF.CALC_GUAR_RBT_AMT * -1,\nDFUP.CALC_SELL_DISPNS_FEE_AMT = DF.CALC_SELL_DISPNS_FEE_AMT * -1,\nDFUP.CALC_BUY_DISPNS_FEE_AMT = DF.CALC_BUY_DISPNS_FEE_AMT * -1\nFROM #$EDWOwner#.CLM_F CF INNER JOIN #$EDWOwner#.DRUG_CLM_PRICE_F DF ON DF.CLM_ID = CF.CLM_ADJ_FROM_CLM_ID\nWHERE CF.SRC_SYS_CD = 'OPTUMRX' and CF.CLM_STTUS_CD = 'A08'  and CF.CLM_ID = DFUP.CLM_ID;\n\ncommit;\nJobName: IdsEdwDrugClmPriceFLoad\n\nThis job loads group count data into EDW table - DRUG_CLM_PRICE_F\nCalled from: IdsEdwDrugClmPriceFCntl\nLoad File from IdsEdwDrugClmPriceFExtr Job"
